=Description=

"Open Geneva is... 

... a non-profit association whose mission is to promote and stimulate open innovation in Greater Geneva by bringing together a community of 2,500 innovators and innovators, bringing their ideas to life, communicating about their projects and supporting their development.

Open Geneva supports the inclusive innovation. The program is designed for everyone, and promotes the development and acceleration of concrete solutions to improve daily life and life in society!

'''Open Geneva organizes and coordinates the Greater Geneva Open Innovation Festival since 2017'''. This innovation highlight is for all those who wish to commit themselves to the future. Dozens of free hackathons, workshops and conferences are taking place in Greater Geneva to find solutions to challenges related to social innovation, sustainable development, global health, media and digital transformation."

